{"tid":1870580,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【醫護罷工】梁振英批李國麟「黨性凌駕人性」　促余慧明馬上辭職","createTime":"2020-02-09T02:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T04:19:24.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c801d6328a36d9f00d8f5d35002c841a7b038f71","tid":1870580,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3975452/org/33fed4ac9cd0649d5e0730893b9697b6.jpg/He59mKpja25nRCZPyC3wm-QdlufjzQSvV7y1Qle8tUI?v=w1440r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3975452%2Forg%2F33fed4ac9cd0649d5e0730893b9697b6.jpg%2FHe59mKpja25nRCZPyC3wm-QdlufjzQSvV7y1Qle8tUI%3Fv%3Dw1440r16_9&h=5fcff149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情持續，醫管局員工陣線早前一連五日罷工，要求政府及醫管局回應全面封關、醫護人員裝備不足等問題，工會昨晚（7日）宣布不會延長罷工。<br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席梁振英連日發文狙擊罷工行動，他今日再於Facebook表示，立法會衛生服務界議員李國麟指，護士協會下周二將商討是否要發起工業行動支援，包括罷工及按章工作，批評是「繼續以黨性凌駕人性，因此參加罷工的人員一定要面對後果，否則沒完沒了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3975481/org/58cdc7afe7381136bd72ef209df87048.png/uobB7AmarbpyvLemXjGef9o8rqyMMoytIV4MuSFeDLk?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3975481%2Forg%2F58cdc7afe7381136bd72ef209df87048.png%2FuobB7AmarbpyvLemXjGef9o8rqyMMoytIV4MuSFeDLk%3Fv%3Dw640&h=e681167a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3975480/org/61f4a002441d9e71dd467a5ced6c1b93.png/aNwRNjVbN9S1snGAkOvy32mr5qhOP8uefvP0TH7z9Ew?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3975480%2Forg%2F61f4a002441d9e71dd467a5ced6c1b93.png%2FaNwRNjVbN9S1snGAkOvy32mr5qhOP8uefvP0TH7z9Ew%3Fv%3Dw640&h=cce7e910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁振英在帖文指，身兼香港護士協會主席的李國麟今早在電台節目上表示，護士協會下星期二會舉行緊急會員大會，商討是否要發起工業行動支援，協會的中央委員會已經商討不同方案，包括罷工及按章工作。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英批評，「醫護罷過一次了，失敗了，還要搞？李國麟等泛民議員和泛民工會繼續以黨性凌駕人性。因此參加罷工的人員一定要面對後果，否則沒完沒了。」<br />\n<br />\n梁振英今早在另一帖文又指，醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明應該馬上辭職。他指出，余慧明在會員投票前，堅持要繼續罷工，「會員投票不達標，就延長投票時間，最後還是失敗。在宣布投票結果時表示，以沉重心情宣布不會延長罷工」。他質疑，投票結果說明大多數會員和余慧明在這重大問題上的立場相反，「作為主席，可以不辭職嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3975453/org/c03f0c5f7f6836c25795c3ca0c608f2f.jpg/N_1tKYc1uelEVcuAgeISFwSVdwScVGspyvHpZ8rx6Wc?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3975453%2Forg%2Fc03f0c5f7f6836c25795c3ca0c608f2f.jpg%2FN_1tKYc1uelEVcuAgeISFwSVdwScVGspyvHpZ8rx6Wc%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=215d2be9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98b71b7aefecdf604bb0d1261f15e56944b61e13","tid":1870580,"uid":74646,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:50:08.000Z","msg":"可以，你見李慧琼都冇辭職啦"},{"pid":"2741eae5121ce0ee5e91e283cac2e0ca0c280b99","tid":1870580,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩，去武漢啦你"},{"pid":"8f55c137a9bd2575aae7e337a62efcc5a3e4b412","tid":1870580,"uid":67896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"98b71b7aefecdf604bb0d1261f15e56944b61e13","tid":1870580,"uid":74646,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:50:08.000Z","msg":"可以，你見李慧琼都冇辭職啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:52:28.000Z","msg":"秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29eb430ed355a6095ac9aa22f805ca2d3a7478d8","tid":1870580,"uid":130060,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c801d6328a36d9f00d8f5d35002c841a7b038f71","tid":1870580,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3975452/org/33fed4ac9cd0649d5e0730893b9697b6.jpg/He59mKpja25