elEVcuAgeISFwSVdwScVGspyvHpZ8rx6Wc%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=215d2be9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T02:55:05.000Z","msg":"呢條撚屌 廢老7少陣當幫忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8b0fbf7928b2e0ca9695f787f677af387e32c0","tid":1870580,"uid":87576,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"咁林鄭幾時走???"},{"pid":"95b52e56b6ef85f356e9e2fa9cccfc205f87d368","tid":1870580,"uid":128117,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"黨性凌駕人性<br />\n<br />\n講緊佢自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffecf715a2475da554fb4a473208222e421473f","tid":1870580,"uid":140104,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:12:41.000Z","msg":"兜個圈話自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71eaa63d15190840093eb3f919c7bcbdefcc1cbd","tid":1870580,"uid":73365,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"大陸之所以今日咁頭㾗，就係始於狼英帶頭赤化香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前大陸有難香港邊次唔幫/唔能力幫？<br />\n將香港變成大陸一部份咪一齊仆街"},{"pid":"67757d94accc8237153afea9d48ab8f392367cc5","tid":1870580,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"講緊港共呀😂"},{"pid":"175d24a998ba0d0d124e8ea5343783f919e22015","tid":1870580,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"佢真係唔識架"},{"pid":"ce820f58f3739d4e7404499d01215747c6e5f714","tid":1870580,"uid":113